  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Become immersed in the world of iCarly and fully interact with its awesome cast of personalities\n\nHang out with Carly, Sam and Freddie at locations from the show, such as Groovie Smoothie, the Pacific Place Mall, and even Carly's apartment\n\nCompete in a series of fun challenges and mini-games to help out the gang\n\nHelp with LIVE in 5! Mode by choosing props for the set, adjusting the crew, and and working to make sure the show goes off without a hitch\n\nWith a DSi, use the system's built-in camera to take shots and import images to customize her look and wardrobe in true iCarly style",
